comments: Joseph (DET) moves alongside of Westbrook (LAL) and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Jackson (DET) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
During the screen, Anthony (LAL) and Bey (DET) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Davis (LAL) has his heel in the restricted area when he makes contact with Grant (DET) as the secondary defender on a driving shot attempt, which starts outside the lower defensive box.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in Joseph's (DET) path and marginal contact occurs as they engage and disengage during the pick.
Joseph (DET) is late to establish himself in Horton-Tucker's (LAL) path and makes contact with his body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) legally contests and cleanly blocks Cunningham's (DET) jump shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Cunningham (DET) and cleanly blocks the shot.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Joseph's (DET) path and makes marginal contact with a collapsed forearm.
Joseph (DET) extends his arm out and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Davis' (LAL) arm during his shot near the rim.
Davis (LAL) is established in Grant's (DET) path and absorbs the contact created by Grant as he extends his head into Davis at the end of his drive.
During the inbound, Jackson (DET) establishes himself in a screening position in Davis' (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs as they engage and disengage on the screen.
Davis (LAL) is bring his arms into a vertical position when marginal contact occurs with Grant's (DET) off-arm during his play at the basket.
Joseph (DET) cleanly intercepts the pass intended for Davis (LAL).
Westbrook (LAL) makes clean ball contact to dislodge it from Grant (DET) as he drives toward the basket.

Replay review of the foul called on Davis (LAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Davis (LAL) maintained a legal guarding position as he moved alongside Bey (DET) and the initial foul whistle occurred prior to any travel by Bey.
Joseph (DET) releases his inbounds pass within 5 seconds.
During the inbounds, Horton-Tucker (LAL) and Cunningham (LAL) engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Bradley (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Grant (DET) during his post shot attempt.
Cunningham (DET) and Horton-Tucker (LAL) come together and marginal contact occurs after the inbounds pass.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) brings the ball past half court within 8 seconds.
Joseph (DET) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Horton-Tucker (LAL) and Jackson (DET) cleanly blocks the shot.
After the clean block, Jackson (DET) avoids contact with the ball after stepping out of bounds and Joseph (DET) legally saves it.
Bey (DET) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
Joseph (DET) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
Davis (LAL) cleanly intercepts the inbounds pass intended for Bey (DET).
